              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18240064030211073667">A light but compelling account of the design and construction of the Duomo di Firenze. There are many more detailed (and perhaps more reliable) writings on Brunelleschi and the dome (Saalman, Hartt, etc.) but none are more inspiring.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

